||Rules Instance Record|##|||Define, assess and refine the rules and thresholds used in customer case determination and resolution activity to ensure decision making is appropriate and equitable||||||IO|IO|O|||
|||Customer Case Decision Criterion|##||Definition of the basis for customer case evaluation||||||IO|IO|O|||
||||Customer Case Decision Criterion Definition||Definition of the applicable subject/criterion to be considered in case evaluation (e.g. documentary evidence, customer/merchant history, projected relationship impact, financial cost/projected revenue impact, reputational impact)||||||IO|IO|O|||
||||Customer Case Decision Criterion Rules||Specific rules, thresholds and parameter values to be applied in case evaluation for the criterion||||||IO|IO|O|||
|||Customer Case Decision Criterion Analysis|##||Analysis of the impact of the criterion in practice that is used to recalibrate associated rules||||||IO|IO|O|||
||||Customer Case Decision Criterion History||Sample case examples that apply the criterion that are used to evaluate the impact and re-calibrate the associated rules as appropriate||||||IO|IO|O|||
||||Customer Case Decision Criterion Analysis||Record of the sensitivity/tuning evaluations and adjustments made to the rule settings for the criterion||||||IO|IO|O|||
