||||Customer Case Service Statistic Value||The statistical analysis that can include historical and trended views of the activity|||||||||IO|IO|O
||||Customer Case Service Statistic Interpretation||The evaluation of the root cause or comparative assessments of the analysis|||||||||IO|IO|O
